description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Procurement Category Suport Specialist Ad + Presentation Title&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Would you like to join an ambitious procurement organisation supporting our Category Work streams and our customer team with the development and implementation of their future strategies and targets for the benefit of our members?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires you to lead sourcing strategies across multiple work streams, contribute to the development of Category Strategies and provide expert advice both internally and externally to our customers on the most appropriate compliant route to market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for highly skilled, competent individual to join our exciting team to develop a best in class procurement activity, managing end-to-end tender processes in accordance with Public Contract Regulations 2015, developing award recommendations and finalising contract sign-off.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for individuals who are passionate about procurement, leading on continuous improvements with a flair for excellence and attention to detail.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this senior role, the candidate must be comfortable with working both autonomously and within a team. The candidate will be required to show they can work effectively and efficiently, with minimal supervision and to demonstrate the value they add to the organisation on a continuing basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRESENTATION TITLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“Describe how you carried out and managed a medium to large scale procurement exercise within the last 12 months. Please pay particular details your responsibilities, how you managed the exercise, rationale for the procurement route taken, outcome and lessons learned from your experience”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 17th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview date: 27th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAdam JaroszJob titleProcurement Shared Services DirectorEmail addressadam.jarosz@lpp.nhs.ukAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information on this exciting opportunity, please contact Adam Jarosz - adam.jarosz@lpp.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
